	* clfswm.lisp (read-conf-file): Read configuration in
	$HOME/.clfswmrc or in /etc/clfswmrc or in
	$XDG_CONFIG_HOME/clfswm/clfswmrc.
	(xdg-config-home): Return the content of $XDG-CONFIG-HOME (default
	to $HOME/.config/).

